TopicTitle: MISSING PART for craft warp drive vessel

Articles.Content:
Welcome to the forums!

Have you removed (or installed) any mods recently? You're missing a small decoupler from a mod, but that's all I can really tell you.

It looks like a decoupler from Deadly Reentry mod. If you used it for this craft and then removed mod with all its parts - it surely won't load. Get mod back and either keep using it or load vessel, install stock decoupler and then you can remove mod again.
